{
  "stem": "747.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't help, but sorry, this-- And then what the Russians did to them and, sort of they're telling me stories, console me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, don't worry, your parents will be back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, this is just rumors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew that it was not rumors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I wanted to tell a little bit of my experiences, by that time, I was fat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was never in my life was so heavy-- that being on starvation diet for so many months in Germany, the American soldiers started to bring us food, and we were eating like pigs, day and night.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I got a stomach like in nine months pregnant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Wasn't healthy, but this was very--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came home with a big stomach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, look, she-- she was never so fat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How could it be so bad, if you look so good?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, I just didn't feel like, after a while, to explain my story, because I-- I saw on their faces that they don't believe me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was just the guilt, or boredom, or whatever, they were not interested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I decided that this is not my home anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is not my country, they kicked me out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just don't want to have anything to do with it anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we decided to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had told me an anecdote about a woman that you saw walking in the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, well, that was-- that was one of really-- the last of-- of-- of the knife cut into me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the second day, I walked in the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was so strange, everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Szerencs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a young woman came toward me, wearing my mother's best dress-- a beautiful grey, wool dress, what I made for her.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
